         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00001-000-00005"/>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Ich wohne »<rs ref="#pmb40154" type="place">Hôtel Neuhauser</rs>«</p><p>Wo wohnen Sie?</p><p>Ich habe infamen Sonnenbrand, »die Sonne« »die Sonne«.</p><p>Grüßen Sie mir <rs ref="#pmb12740" type="person">Schwarzkopf</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Loris</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb2167" type="person">Salten</rs>.</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer><postscript><dateline><date>19 Mai 91</date></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
